      "text": "あっ、{user}さん、こんにちは～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello there‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7150112311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんなら、今外出してますわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re looking for Rui and Sumire‚ they’re out now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.657528305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうや\nぶぶ漬けでも食べながらお待ちになります？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚\nhow about we eat some bubuzuke or something while we wait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ぶぶ漬けって……え？　……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bubuzuke? What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確か京都の人がお客を追い返す時の常套句だったよな？\n……鈴村さん、もしかして怒ってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn’t that a standard expression Kyoto people use for getting rid of guests?\nSuzumura… are you angry with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
